TKPlayer for Windows is capable of playing all media files without requiring additional decoders on your PC.
 TKPlayer is able to play popular media formats in high quality, including MPEG, MP4, H.264, M4V, MKV, MOV, 
FLV, AVI, 3GP, DV, DVD, 4K, 3D, AAC, MP3, M4R, OGG, WMA, etc., as well as high resolution movies, such as 3D,
4K UHD and more. It's also able to play movies with CC (Closed Captions) subtitles and provide additional settings 
for media playback so that you can adjust video brightness, aspect ratio, set audio equalizer, add subtitles, or 
capture the screen as JPG and PNG with ease.